         <h2>My philosophy and Style</h2>
          <div class="w3-container w3-theme-l5" style="font-size:x-large">
            <p>Learning varies with individuals; no one method provides a universally ideal approach.  However, any technique that generates student interest and maximizes student engagement is always beneficial.  My methods for maximizing interest and engagement include the following.<p>
             <ul><li>Deliberately expressing my passion for everything earth science.</li>
                 <li>Providing metaphors and analogies using real world items and topics important to students when explaining complex ideas</li>
                 <li>Minimize any actual lecturing.  Instead I use questions and guide answers.  Yes, I expect everyone to participate!</li>
                 <li>Solve problems in class using small groups, selected to ensure every group has a broad range of backgrounds and opinions.</li>
              </ul>
          </div>
